<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10022284>
    dc:description "FIGURES 153a–155b. Ventral view of 153a). Massilieurodes myricae Jensen, 2001; Front and back of holotype slides of 153b). Massilieurodes myricae Jensen, 2001; Ventral view of 154a). Carolinaia (Carolinaia) floridensis Remaudière & Muñoz Viveros, 1993; Front and back of holotype slides of 154b). Carolinaia (Carolinaia) floridensis Remaudière & Muñoz Viveros, 1993; Ventral view of 155a). Thripsaphis (Thripsaphis) polytricha Quednau, 2010; Front and back of holotype slides of 155b). Thripsaphis (Thripsaphis) polytricha Quednau, 2010. Scale bar 153a = 0.5 mm, scale bars 154a & 155a = 1 mm, scale bars 153b, 154b & 155b = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10022284/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

